oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: See the Pinnacle
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: View of one automobile driving down U.S. Highway 25-E in Cumberland Gap. Several signs are on the side of the road, including a historical marker and an advertisement for the Pinnacle. A few small buildings are near one sign.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
